full_text: Only thing I’ll say about this…If I was @bakermayfield I’d stay quiet, show up to #Browns Off-Season program and force their hand to move on from me or pay me 18 million to sit there and do nothing

Great way for @dariusgarland22 & young #Cavs team to get a taste of playoffs, play Championship quality team in 1 game series, and then battle another young team with rising star PG, but winning the home game and getting into a real playoff series is crucial!
